article_title: UnitedHealth's Latest Blow To Fee-For-Service Medicine: 6 Percent Off Doctor Costs

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: As the Affordable Care Act, government and private insurers push doctors and hospitals away from fee-for-service medicine, the nation’s largest insurer, UnitedHealth Group, (UNH) says it’s seeing more results.
